Below is a brief explanation of each java file and its purpose.

FilePermission.java            --       Purpose: Manages file permissions for users and roles.
IntegratedShell.java           --       Purpose: To integrate all the features into an unified shell.
PagingSystem.java              --       Purpose: Implements the paging system with FIFO and LRU algorithms.
ProcessSynchronization.java    --       Purpose: Implements Producer-Consumer problem with Semaphores.
ShellCommands.java             --       Purpose: Implements the core shell functionalities and built-in commands.
ShellScheduler.java            --       Purpose: Implements process scheduling policies (Round-Robin and Priority scheduling).
UserAuthentication.java        --       Purpose: Handles User authentication.
